  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Ninja Kid (regional port of GeGeGe no Kitaro: Yokai Daimakyou) is a NES platformer published by Bandai. As with Super Mario Bros 2, Ninja Kid went through some significant changes for its US release.",
